OL,6,FSix sources corroborated allegations
OL,7,Fabout Gerry Adams that were made by an
OL,8,Fanonymous contributor to a BBC
OL,9,Fdocumentary, lawyers representing the
OL,10,Fbroadcaster have told a libel trial.
OL,12,FMr Adams is suing the BBC over what he
OL,13,Fhas deemed to be a "grievous smear"
OL,14,Fmade by a confidential source in a
OL,15,FSpotlight documentary that alleged he
OL,16,Fhad sanctioned the killing of a former
OL,17,FSinn Fein official who turned out to
OL,18,Fbe an informant.
