OL,3,CBBC insist Adams allegation
OL,4,Ccoroborated by a total of six sources
OL,6,FIn the programme, a man identified as
OL,7,F"Martin" who says he was a former
OL,8,Fagent for Special Branch, claims that
OL,9,Fthe shooting was sanctioned by the
OL,10,Fpolitical and military leadership of
OL,11,Fthe IRA and said Mr Adams "gives the
OL,12,Ffinal say".
OL,14,FMr Adams's legal team says his
OL,15,Freputation as a "peacemaker" had
OL,16,Fsuffered an "unjustified" attack
OL,17,Fbecause of the broadcast of the BBC
OL,18,Fprogramme, and the online article with
OL,19,Fthe headline: "Gerry Adams 'sanctioned
OL,20,FDenis Donaldson killing'."
