OL,4,Ccoroborated by a total of six sources
OL,6,FHe said he arrived to this conclusion
OL,7,Fafter being tasked with putting
OL,8,Ftogether an "impartial and
OL,9,Findependent" report by Mr Adams's
OL,10,Flegal team, which examined discovery
OL,11,Finformation for the case,
OL,12,Fcorrespondence between the BBC and Mr
OL,13,FAdams's legal team before and after
OL,14,Fthe broadcast, and editorial standards
OL,15,Fas well as the broadcast and article
OL,16,Fat issue in the action.
OL,18,FMr O'Loan has previously held roles
OL,19,Finvolving senior editorial
OL,20,Fresponsibility, including by
OL,21,Festablishing Sky News.
